{"tid":2516363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首富換位｜福布斯實時富豪榜 曾毓群晉身香港首富","createTime":"2021-05-04T14:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T14:52:10.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5cf62f380b0f0d254ee02c6f9155d6b63f8a4a7f","tid":2516363,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2948602/20210505OG-W002_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2948602%2F20210505OG-W002_1024.jpg&h=a5076515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n福布斯實時富豪榜顯示，電動汽車電池制造商寧德時代的董事局主席曾毓群晉身香港首富，其身家達345億美元（約2,679億港元），超越第二位長和的李嘉誠和第三位恒基的李兆基。<br />\n<br />\n隨着對電動汽車需求升溫，寧德時代過去一年股價飆升逾150%，最新市值達到9,042億元人民幣。52歲的曾毓群生於福建，他通過瑞廷時代，持有寧德時代24.53%的股份。<br />\n<br />\n按福布斯實時數據，李嘉誠的身家為344億美元，比曾毓群僅低1億美元，李兆基身家有321億美元。"},{"pid":"bfa86965872c34c63413bb7b7dda73404b1abc7a","tid":2516363,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2948602/首富換位｜福布斯實時富豪榜%20曾毓群晉身香港首富\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2948602%2F%E9%A6%96%E5%AF%8C%E6%8F%9B%E4%BD%8D%EF%BD%9C%E7%A6%8F%E5%B8%83%E6%96%AF%E5%AF%A6%E6%99%82%E5%AF%8C%E8%B1%AA%E6%A6%9C%2520%E6%9B%BE%E6%AF%93%E7%BE%A4%E6%99%89%E8%BA%AB%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A6%96%E5%AF%8C&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=284b4567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2948602/首富換位｜福布斯實時富豪榜%20曾毓群晉身香港首富</a>"},{"pid":"dcde26479bcbc3ea2ba8ad35fd546301a06808a9","tid":2516363,"uid":158480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:52:10.000Z","msg":"支那狗黎，邊比香港？"}]}